Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:40.98,Next Episode,,0,0,0,,Nabudúce...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:29.76,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vidíme sa zajtra!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.69,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasne, v škole.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:32.78,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:34.22,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.32,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:37.85,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:40.92,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasne!
